        <Parent_String>linear perspective (technique) [300056348], perspective (technique) [300056340], perspective and shading techniques [300053413], image-making processes and techniques [300053159], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
